{"tid":936350,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩可以令你一秒著火...","createTime":"2018-12-10T16:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T04:02:29.000Z","uid":225090,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"3f699a59b36b066002697512b8f1d25ccaf47633","tid":936350,"uid":225090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:29:24.000Z","msg":"話說岩先去食晚飯<br />\n本來我心情都好好<br />\n點知一坐到落去<br />\n隔離果枱三個講普通話嘅bitch<br />\n係到傾韓星 （其實我都唔係好聽得明佢地啲普通話 但略略都聽到啲）<br />\n好啦 我見到佢地個鍋都熄曬火 <br />\n心諗應該好快走 <br />\n點知 我同朋友個鍋到左 <br />\n食到咁上下 發覺唔對路  <br />\n佢地食完都係咁大大聲傾大大聲笑<br />\n我地已經係咁啤佢地 <br />\n佢地依然係咁 <br />\n當時真係著曬火 想一個鍋車埋佢地到<br />\n但理性嘅我無咁做到<br />\n一直沉住氣食曬佢 默默地比錢走人<br />\n佢地係我地走果時都未走 <br />\n我心入面已經唔知講左幾多句粗口<br />\n究竟係因為普通話先咁反感定因為佢地太嘈而咁反感呢 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我嘅重點係 <br />\n如果再遇到咁嘅情形 點樣可以保持心境開朗地食完餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e3f4355546bb6ce00832319a2409faa8cabbda","tid":936350,"uid":29080,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:30:11.000Z","msg":"汽油加火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58545f5a492204cebf7a85c702641cbd581d9ec","tid":936350,"uid":121610,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:33:33.000Z","msg":"開佢拖啦 依家搭親地鐵有大陸人行埋黎都會開㬹行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96de34cff4bfff76de709b65065217e8b4badb6","tid":936350,"uid":159444,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:33:53.000Z","msg":"666<br />\n聽到就想打鳩條友"},{"pid":"796871f4